text: "All the Right Moves" is a 2009 song by American pop rock band OneRepublic and is the lead single from their second studio album Waking Up. It went to the top 10 in Austria, Belgium, the Czech Republic, Ireland, Israel, Luxembourg, New Zealand, Norway, Slovakia and Switzerland and went to top 20 in Finland, France, Germany, Hungary, Sweden and the United States. It also missed the top 20 in Canada. == Track listing == *;CD single #"All the Right Moves" – 3:59 #"All the Right Moves" (Filthy Dukes remix) – 5:05 == References == Category:2009 songs Category:OneRepublic songs
